    "description": "欢迎来到奇妙的乌托邦世界。在这里，人类与忠诚热情的机器人和谐共处，生活一直都完美无瑕。<br><br>再过几天，最新的机器人控制系统就要启动了，一切都照计划进行，除非忽然出现惨烈的事故，或者什么天大的阴谋……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/fd8587e23f88ccbe039840c97e99a7e6.poster.avif?t=1764675129\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/fd8587e23f88ccbe039840c97e99a7e6.webm?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/fd8587e23f88ccbe039840c97e99a7e6.mp4?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>科学发展的脚步不可阻挡，秘密实验也随之展开，催生了无数骇人的变异体和机器，还有能力超强的机器人，可如今，它们忽然开始反抗自己的造物主。只有你能阻止它们，揭露理想世界背后隐藏的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/b11fd3722bf23cdc5e2f08b371b38257.poster.avif?t=1764675129\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/b11fd3722bf23cdc5e2f08b371b38257.webm?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/b11fd3722bf23cdc5e2f08b371b38257.mp4?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>生死之战，一触即发。善用具有各种能力的试制手套、形形色色的刀剑和走在科学前沿的尖端武器，在爆炸的火光之中杀出一条血路。针对独特敌人制定最佳战术，结合手上的技能和资源，升级装备，利用环境条件，克服重重挑战，为正义而战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/da42f4152da901d5ad7f219df95c37dd.poster.avif?t=1764675129\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/da42f4152da901d5ad7f219df95c37dd.webm?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668580/extras/da42f4152da901d5ad7f219df95c37dd.mp4?t=1764675129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>•\t美妙而又疯狂的乌托邦世界<br>•\t棘手的战斗难度，恢弘壮观的战斗场面，满屏都是血浆<br>•\t用各种技能和尖端武器暴揍高大的机器和变异体<br>•\t升级武器库和装备",
